Introduction

Eunji is a South Korean singer, Songwriter-composer, Actress and a former Radio DJ under IST Entertainment. Eunji debuted as a member of APINK on April 19, 2011 with the group's first mini album Seven Springs of Apink.

She made her debut as an actress in the tvN drama "Reply 1997" that aired in 2012.

She made her debut as a musical actress in 2012 with the musical 'Legally Blonde'

She made her debut as a Solo artist on April 18, 2016 with her first mini album Dream.
